{"tid":291224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"狗義工\"蕃薯兵團\"開fb page上報吸光環籌錢 實質虐狗任由狗隻被強姦咬死","createTime":"2017-06-20T11:45:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T06:45:02.000Z","uid":22349,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a2201abf7691859170f1f9a1dd503ec34dff4d2d","tid":291224,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T11:45:52.000Z","msg":"狗義工：Kei Lam 阿基 (花名：薯爸）<br />\n               黃先生<br />\n<br />\n人物背景：<br />\n薯爸與黃先生同住<br />\n<br />\n薯爸開設Facebook page &quot;新蕃薯兵團&quot; (前名：蕃薯兵團）<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/新蕃薯兵團-1317882114900498/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2F%E6%96%B0%E8%95%83%E8%96%AF%E5%85%B5%E5%9C%98-1317882114900498%2F&d=KLaJfgYMxVvWvyTkbsFuLpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=d736a677\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/新蕃薯兵團-1317882114900498/</a><br />\n<br />\n薯爸曾接受E 週刊訪問<br />\n<a href=\"https://eweekly.hk/article/_title/他來自江湖_蕃薯兵團改變我_jv15anbvl3c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Feweekly.hk%2Farticle%2F_title%2F%E4%BB%96%E4%BE%86%E8%87%AA%E6%B1%9F%E6%B9%96_%E8%95%83%E8%96%AF%E5%85%B5%E5%9C%98%E6%94%B9%E8%AE%8A%E6%88%91_jv15anbvl3c&d=KLaJfgYMxVvWvyTkbsFuLpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=366bd852\" target=\"_blank\">https://eweekly.hk/article/_title/他來自江湖_蕃薯兵團改變我_jv15anbvl3c</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5mtJWUXzR6U\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5mtJWUXzR6U&d=KLaJfgYMxVvWvyTkbsFuLpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=d2984833\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5mtJWUXzR6U</a><br />\n<br />\n事件：<br />\n<br />\n1. 黃先生罪狀：<br />\n<br />\n黃先生寄住在薯爸家中，養了兩隻雪橇犬Chivas和Rosee、一隻貓。其中Rosee還是在個半月前才由黃先生領養回來。另有一隻松鼠狗因為年老，已於今年2月左右病死。後來，黃先生領養狗仔「咖啡妹」，大半年後狗仔變成皮包骨，嚴重營養不良。知情人士指，黃先生已經失業幾個月，甚少餵自己所養的貓狗，「試過因為薯爸兩日沒回家，結果兩雪橇犬兩日都沒有吃到一餐」，而那隻貓也試過三日才餵一次，貓砂亦十日不換。<br />\n<br />\n近日，薯爸的狗B亦被狗咬死，事後黃生稱因為睡覺沒察覺，結果薯爸趕黃生出屋。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hkanimalpost.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/RKSR-RLMY-VJD.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkanimalpost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2FRKSR-RLMY-VJD.jpg&d=KLaJfgYMxVvWvyTkbsFuLpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=f1d7cad1\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.hkanimalpost.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/RKSR-RLMY-VJD.jpg</a><br />\n由於咖啡妹出現嚴重營養不良，於是由義工Iris帶回照顧。<br />\n<br />\n義工 Iris表示，曾在「咖啡妹」出院後報愛協，但愛協職員稱由於黃先生有帶狗看醫生，故難以作出控告。<br />\n<br />\n繼咖啡妹在今年4月底由義工Iris接走外，現時兩狗一貓都已救出，其中Rosee由義工暫托，而Chivas則返回前主人身邊。"},{"pid":"e45536ccb35b1193c2bd706d0bbb61dde4db74e9","tid":291224,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T11:46:33.000Z","msg":"咖啡妹：<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkanimalpost.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/RKSR-RLMY-VJD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkanimalpost.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F05%2FRKSR-RLMY-VJD.jpg&h=b1d9c0c1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a2f37175ed1c37951bf6e6e72fcfffdc59dda7b4","tid":291224,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T12:01:29.000Z","msg":"2. 薯爸罪狀<br />\n<br />\n多隻狗仔起佢照顧下死左！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n轉載from fb受害人sunny cheung<br />\n<br />\n大家好，我今日要公開<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">妮妮</span></strong>既身世！2016年6月，因為一個村民話要棄狗，一鄰居係facebook出貼搵領養，之後薯爸話可以接！<br />\n<br />\n鄰居好開心同我講話佢好好，好出名愛狗，收流好多浪浪，佢地有個page叫蕃薯兵團。<br />\n<br />\n於是我地就相信呢個人，薯爸就接左第一隻狗，即後來既Diana! <br />\n<br />\n隔了個幾2個月，應該係8月頭，村民ee又話執到一隻狗B（大概3-4個月)受傷被綁到頸流哂血，於是去睇左獸醫已醫返好，由於ee屋企已有好多貓狗，而且環境比較惡劣，所以就將狗轉托於薯爸，如果有人領養就出，冇人領養佢就接左狗仔做蕃薯兵團成員，本來都擔心佢太多狗所以希望揾到其他人領養，但都冇人問津，蕃薯爸就將佢列入左兵團成員之一，佢叫做妮妮！<br />\n<br />\n就係咁，一路到lucky事件發生，我開始擔心妮妮，我有問過薯爸妮妮絕左育未，佢話有，我就天真地以為妮妮會安全。直至發生咬死狗B事件後，有人pm話我知：妮妮已經死左！！！<br />\n<br />\n妮妮係有左，生左幾隻BB，之後全家死哂！<br />\n有人仲send左好多妮妮生前既相俾我，佢個樣好無助，身上亦有疥癬！<br />\n<br />\n我之所以托妮妮俾薯爸係因為姨姨度D環境好差，怕妮妮會全身皮膚亦冇＄帶佢睇醫生。<br />\n<br />\n薯爸亦講過：係佢度一定三餐溫飽，有病會睇醫生，養到老！<br />\n<br />\n但..呢個人究竟做左D乜，點解要害死可愛又嗲人既妮妮，仲要害佢全家死哂！！我真係好心痛，係我親手將妮妮送去俾死神！係我冇盡力幫佢尋家諗住有人收養就算！我既責任好大！我唔敢話俾ee知，我怕佢老人家自責，怕佢同我一樣失眠！！！而呢一個人，佢絕對唔適合再養狗，我唔想再有其他狗受害，唔想妮妮死左都冇人知，甚至連我都唔知佢幾時死，係點死！！"},{"pid":"bcea9daeaea63dd5b2eaf4a2acfeadd54e7974ac","tid":291224,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T12:09:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/200927_17a34f683b13458283bdc1114cba8461.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F200927_17a34f683b13458283bdc1114cba8461.jpg&h=a3010e08&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/200928_5a8cbdc64c2e7f5fdf9a9a0de4830714.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F200928_5a8cbdc64c2e7f5fdf9a9a0de4830714.jpg&h=f1617714&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2e73a98b45c6fb229dcd50d4d8325f9a394f361b","tid":291224,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T12:18:00.000Z","msg":"薯爸罪狀二：遺棄狗仔呀黃<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/201627_0eb85f79b91c7e55259372b020f0adc5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F201627_0eb85f79b91c7e55259372b020f0adc5.jpg&h=bf4a0698&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n薯爸罪狀三：任由狗仔粟米被大狗強姦，狗bb 亦通通被其他狗咬死<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/201748_060495f635524b07e28734549c3925af.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F201748_060495f635524b07e28734549c3925af.jpg&h=72e0412b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5e9d15899d30e65cbd0574831e61eabc7d329baf","tid":291224,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-20T12:22:56.000Z","msg":"薯爸女朋友Ching Ching罪狀：<br />\n強詞奪理為薯爸開脫罪狀，推曬落黃先生身上<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/20/202055_7b4b227fea17dfbb7377bbd7e8e6b95e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F20%2F202055_7b4b227fea17